'''Node.js''' is a [[cross-platform]], [[Open-source software|open-source]] [[JavaScript]]
[[Runtime environment|runtime environment]] that can run on [[Microsoft Windows|Windows]],
[[Linux]], [[Unix]], [[macOS]], and more. Node.js runs on the [[V8 (JavaScript engine)|V8]]
[[JavaScript engine]], and executes JavaScript code outside a [[web browser]].

